OL,6,FConcerns were raised about an
OL,7,Fevangelical priest welcoming "scantily
OL,8,Fclad, lycra-wearing" followers to his
OL,9,Fhome, a sex abuse trial has heard.
OL,11,FChristopher Brain, 68, is accused of
OL,12,Fassaulting 13 women while leader of
OL,13,Fthe the Nine O'Clock Service (NOS),
OL,14,Fpart of the Church of England, in
OL,15,FSheffield.
OL,17,FHe is on trial at Inner London Crown
OL,18,FCourt charged with one count of rape
OL,19,Fand 36 counts of indecent assault
OL,20,Fbetween 1981 and 1995.
