OL,6,FBrain, from Wilmslow, Cheshire, denies
OL,7,Fthe charges.
OL,9,FGiving evidence on Wednesday, Mark
OL,10,FStibbe, who was a curate at St
OL,11,FThomas's Church in Sheffield where NOS
OL,12,Fmembers met, said there were
OL,13,Fmisgivings about its direction and
OL,14,Fwhat was going on at Brain's home.
OL,16,FDr Stibbe recalled concerns being
OL,17,Fraised by another church official
OL,18,Fabout Brain.
