OL,6,FHe said: "He brought up the negative
OL,7,Foptics, potentially anyway, of
OL,8,Fscantily clad, lycra-wearing pretty
OL,9,Fyoung women as he put it coming to and
OL,10,Ffrom Chris Brain's house on a regular
OL,11,Fbasis to perform 'domestic duties'."
OL,13,FThe witness said the man got a
OL,14,F"roasting" for asking whether there
OL,15,Fwas "anything untoward" about it.
OL,17,FDr Stibbe also recalled "a lot of
OL,18,Fcontroversy" over the Greenbelt
OL,19,FChristian arts festival "into which
OL,20,FNOS had poured many hours and many
OL,21,Fthousands of pounds".
