OL,6,FAfter leaving NOS, he said he returned
OL,7,Fto attend a service when a member of
OL,8,Fhis congregation expressed concerns.
OL,10,FHe said: "My view at the time was that
OL,11,Fit was extremely disturbing and that
OL,12,Fmy friend who had said it was
OL,13,Fdisturbing was correct.
OL,15,F"The reason I found it disturbing is
OL,16,Fthat the things that had been reported
OL,17,Ffrom the Greenbelt Festival about
OL,18,Fgirls gyrating in scantily clad
OL,19,Fcostume in a worship context, that is
OL,20,Fwhat I was seeing in this context."
