OL,6,FThe prosecution alleges Brain ran NOS
OL,7,Fas a cult and sexually assaulted a
OL,8,F"staggering number" of women
OL,9,Ffollowers, exerting control over their
OL,10,Flives and ostracising them from
OL,11,Ffriends and family.
OL,13,FThe court has heard a "homebase team"
OL,14,Fwas set up to "care for" Brain `
OL,15,Freferred to as the Lycra Lovelies or
OL,16,Fthe Lycra Nuns.
OL,18,FWitnesses reported seeing the
OL,19,Fdefendant surrounded by attractive
OL,20,Fwomen in lingerie at his home looking
OL,21,Fafter his needs.
