OL,6,FDr Stibbe said he wrote to the then
OL,7,FBishop of Sheffield to ask about
OL,8,Foversight of NOS.
OL,10,F"It seemed to me that it had drifted
OL,11,Fso far away from being a Christian
OL,12,Fritual and Christian service and there
OL,13,Fwere elements of it that deeply
OL,14,Fdisturbed me and I felt it was not
OL,15,Fproperly accountable," he said.
OL,17,F"I do remember saying to him that I
OL,18,Ffelt that if he did not step in and
OL,19,Fdiscern what was truly going on in the
OL,20,Fcongregation that there would be
OL,21,Fdisaster within one year."
